``` go
package main

import "fmt"

type foo struct{}

func (f *foo) greet() {
	if f == nil {
		fmt.Println("who is saying this?")
	}
}

func main() {
	var f *foo = nil
	f.greet()
}
```

The above program compiles and prints `who is saying this?`:

{{True||False}}

``` go
